{"tid":93683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]深圳海關警員自殺　羅湖口岸聯檢樓跳樓身","createTime":"2017-01-24T15:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T07:08:32.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef1412e84e4d0ea3615cd7630586d398df81a1c","tid":93683,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/bkncn-20170124214033451-0124_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170124%2Fbkncn-20170124214033451-0124_05011_001.html&d=WTx8YifNbAy2WvdCmHyJUGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=216124a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/bkncn-20170124214033451-0124_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/photo/bkncn-20170124214033451-0124_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170124%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170124214033451-0124_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=0a096fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳羅湖海關緝私分局黃姓警員，日前在羅湖口岸聯檢樓的7樓墮下身亡。羅湖警方表示，經法醫到場勘驗後，初步判定為跳樓自殺。經查，死者為52歲的黃姓警員，為深圳羅湖海關緝私分局警員。<br />\n<br />\n羅湖警方表示，本月13日下午4時許接報稱，一名男子從羅湖口岸聯檢樓跳下，醫護人員到場後為該男子進行急救，惟經搶救無效死亡。知情者透露，死者黃某為廣東人，1981年加入海關，至今已工作35年，事發前為羅湖海關緝私分局的主任科員。至於其跳樓自殺原因，則有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0434cc58bf8ccab46ca1657e713660df3b97b7","tid":93683,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"583f88dbb187ee19c2eea7af8bc2acd1f48b481e","tid":93683,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:01:21.000Z","msg":"似食死貓"},{"pid":"b4f03ea8dfd52fafb0c3907f2b19afa27f8efbcd","tid":93683,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:47:10.000Z","m